_sText:
Please give me feedback and let me know what you guys think. This isn't my first map. I actually have a ton that I've never distributed. However, I hope to distribute them soon and see what you all think. Just let me know good or bad.

NOTE: There are 28 spawnpoints, and no I didn't put that many on a small map because I'm new at mapping. I did it because a lot of servers maxplayers are anywhere from 24 - 32.

Please remember to leave a comments, stamps, and ratings.

FatGuyLaughing

A.K.A. Fatty
